{"tid":1617111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[都市陷阱師] [多圖] 個細路一野跣低所有人","createTime":"2019-10-03T15:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:27:24.000Z","uid":112405,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7a9cfb93c0da1ac34bfe66556e5ced94c17843","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>序章 &ndash; 波子汽水</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日行街買左一大袋波子同一打汽水, 諗住返屋企整波子汽水。當發現裝波子個膠袋穿左, 我就用膠紙封住/補返個底, 但膠紙太長, 係到揈揈下。咁我就冇理到就繼續行街, 買埋支晾衫竹就打算返屋企。等緊巴士時, 我掛袋波子上支竹到, 順便放支竹埋一邊, 諗住休息下。<br />\n圖示: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dy2FSc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dy2FSc.png&h=1be92315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等左十幾分鐘, 準備上巴士果時, 有個細路就手多多, 一野扯走左條膠紙, 咁個膠袋就成個底穿晒, 啲波子就跌晒落地。然後, 後面追巴士嘅人就踩中啲波子, 跣低晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當堂嚇到連支竹都唔要, 即刻上巴士走人啦。真係唔關我事, 點解而家啲D細路咁百厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭緊巴士時都心有餘悸, 留意住周圍有冇目光望住我。突然, 我眼前一黑&hellip;...<br />\n<br />\n續待......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手寫故，覺得好睇就幫我推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非常歡迎留言交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e757f2d8d1ef4f8b37fcd7fef8c136f67cd8df0a","tid":1617111,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=5cded2d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"0c729dc85e83211734e9db5d10e540c38351c38b","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>第二章 - 求生與陷阱</strong></span><br />\n當我恢復視野, 發現架巴士已經冇晒人, 啲座位仲變到溶溶爛爛。我即刻落車睇下, 發現成個城市都冇晒人!!! 城市、大廈佈滿植物, 周圍都綠油油一片。個世界究竟發生左咩事? <br />\n<br />\n我冷靜落黎, 決定先搞清楚現時係咩日子先。我去到附近一間M記, 拎起入面一包薯條, WTF? 薯條上面生左霉菌, 佔薯條總面積大約30%。根據麥氏薯條鑑年法, 而家即係距離薯條出爐時間約100年......<br />\n<br />\n我快速接受眼前嘅事實, 腦海中只有繼續生存呢個想法。所以, 我決定首先要解決糧食問題。身為聰明人既我, 第一時間去左附近警署搜索有用嘅武器, 卻發現所有槍械火藥都已失效。睇黎, 我要用最原始、方便易整、又可以保存體力嘅方法去捕獵。 從此, 我就走上成為都市陷阱師之路&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"98ce1227619e6221a4171cc7d541a32f2f584b47","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>第三章 - 打狗棒法</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n整個都市成為左廢墟、周圍只有野生動物出沒, 不時傳來野狗嘅叫聲。普通草食動物我唔怕, 但怕野狗。為免成為野狗獵物, 我由自己基地沿路製作幾個陷阱, 以保障自己有一條安全退路。材料都係路上搵到, 包括: 一個鐵欄、一個支撐物(Trigger)、繩、大量竹。<br />\n圖示:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v52u5k2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv52u5k2.png&h=c0bb4e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我跑過後一拉繩, 排竹就會塌落黎, 應該可以截斷追兵。可能仲會好彩扑暈一兩隻狗, 到時就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c817c9bf9a95b0e65c6791cefc8baab0674edb5","tid":1617111,"uid":277595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f027c6559e337aad04859dc23edea990853649a4","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:37:47.000Z","msg":"第四章 - 怒漢拉車<br />\n<br />\n當我嘗試左幾次用M記半發霉食物去吸引獵物, 然後發覺狗也不屌時, 我餓到萌生左一個瘋狂既想法 &mdash;&mdash; 用自己做誘餌&hellip;...<br />\n<br />\n我先用水馬(作用如滑輪)、車仔、長竹、繩, 製作左一個比較主動嘅機關(如圖示), 但前題都係走佬為主 (無事先做到世界冠軍架嘛)<br />\n圖示:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NRLDSX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NRLDSX.png&h=0fcef9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\np.s. <br />\n1. 竹頭要尖, 務求一擊必殺;<br />\n2. 車要收好, 攻擊時突然有一車野追撞過黎, 唔打得都嚇得<br />\n<br />\n前面有一隻野豬, 我保持一段合適距離去挑釁佢。隻嬲嬲豬以每秒9.26米既速度衝向我, 我計好地形同時機, 向後急退並拉動條繩。發動陷阱卡, 車你車你! 一聲哀嚎, 我呢幾日既糧食就有著落了。<br />\n<br />\n之後由於基地附近比較開揚, 我就用左雙閘式設計去建築我既防禦工事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8sSiVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8sSiVg.jpg&h=68ac816e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa588c228217df367c0d8e162dba70365eb944a3","tid":1617111,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"咁得閒FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b9a2cdd379cd7c4d7f8e6a53530a190912e829","tid":1617111,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"Dr Stone"},{"pid":"8468c96657fd0f67ea254345407d2d326c5d02ce","tid":1617111,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a173469142f2d5547650d04d487d7c05c2ed03ab","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>第五章 - 路遺不拾</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有一次出外覓食時, 我畀一隻跑得好快嘅狗追, 由於我個打狗竹陣塌落黎時有2.37秒嘅延遲。當呢隻行動敏捷嘅狗順利避過陷阱時, 我再冇防禦嘅陷阱。最後隻狗撲上黎, 我只好同佢死鬥。雖然用隨身嘅刀殺死左隻狗, 但我都受左唔少傷, 左腳亦都被咬傷, 呢個教訓相當沈重&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n之後我決定係我活動範圍外都用垃圾膠樽鋪滿路面，為自己製造一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵物減速帶</span></strong>。有事上黎，我都有多幾秒走。<br />\n圖示:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KDRzwk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KDRzwk.png&h=af21d8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n續待......"},{"pid":"2eb3fed3bd5282f616fe1c21d5dca68a0b5e1143","tid":1617111,"uid":252609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0611a4bfa62af9ee2f9555e427c65e2aa6a7d908","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊就係最好嘅防守</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但當未有勇氣、力量去對敵物進行主動攻擊時，唯有進行防禦工事。"},{"pid":"a93211f4f6e333597d885aed5a553866b02f8fef","tid":1617111,"uid":112405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2eb3fed3bd5282f616fe1c21d5dca68a0b5e1143","tid":1617111,"uid":252609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"防禦工事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想主角可以一野掟死一隻豬。但勇氣同力量都係需要慢慢訓練出黎。主角係普通人，要升下lv先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9638522d69e09b3e7e8fb17291935f94ae7b39a6","tid":1617111,"uid":327936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab74cf5bc6a0c731b3e9af951c63ebef8b8f5a91","tid":1617111,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的零分重作<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"4e220f581e47feed3981dc66affbe6085e316639","tid":1617111,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"原來個一蚊銀入左黎，我出返去先"},{"pid":"d1ebadbdede69e01def50cb0788b94f141ebc51c","tid":1617111,"uid":68216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"多謝你禁有心 我完全明白你想表達既野 雖然有啲1999<br />\n<br />\n1.一大袋波子其實都幾重<br />\n2. 邊到有禁多竹？<br />\n3. 好似上面巴打講 用人力拉應該個加速度唔夠對狗做成傷害<br />\n<br />\n我覺得 你上面既某啲建議 可以改做係有斜坡既地理位置時候用 當狗